<CSSPadding>
<summary>
The <strong><c>padding</c></strong> <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</see> <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties">shorthand property</see> sets the <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_box_model/Introduction_to_the_CSS_box_model#padding_area">padding area</see> on all four sides of an element at once.
</summary>
<remarks>
<para>EmbedInteractiveExample("pages/css/padding.html")</para><para>An element&amp;apos;s padding area is the space between its content and its border.</para><blockquote class="NOTE"><h5>NOTE</h5><para><strong>Note:</strong> Padding creates extra space within an element. In contrast, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/margin">margin</see> creates extra space <strong>around</strong> an element.</para></blockquote>
<para>-<see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_box_model/Introduction_to_the_CSS_box_model">Introduction to the CSS basic box model</see><br/>-<see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-top">padding-top</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-right">padding-right</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-bottom">padding-bottom</see>, and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-left">padding-left</see>.<br/>-The mapped logical properties: <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-block-start">padding-block-start</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-block-end">padding-block-end</see>, <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-inline-start">padding-inline-start</see>, and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-inline-end">padding-inline-end</see> and the shorthands <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-block">padding-block</see> and <see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-inline">padding-inline</see><br/></para>
<para><seealso href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding"> <em>See also on MDN</em> </seealso></para>
</remarks>
